name: ABOVE & BELOW
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Something is surfacing.

Something wants to surface or is surfacing from below in the depths of your subconscious. Check the other cards you have pulled to give you an indication as to what is surfacing. What’s on the inside needs to be expressed on the outside, what is deep down below wants to be expressed above. 

Let it surface 

Whatever it is, whether it’s something you need to get off your chest, something you need to say to someone or a piece of work you need to create. Our lives are a reflection of what’s going on inside of us and if you are holding back or repressing something for whatever reason that will be reflected in your life.

It’s just below waiting to push through. It wants to surface and so it will surface. It’s coming up out into the light of day,  let it through and out and up. It's part of you and it wants to express itself above ground and out in the open. Let it.

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
